# AMR D convergence Poiseuille with a horizontal Y band, scale 1 template.

Simulation amr_d_poiseuille_yband_scale1 D2Q9

Define scale = 1
Define Fx = 5e-5
Define omega = 1.0
Define rho0 = 1.0

Domain L = 18 x 14  N = 18 x 14
Physics nu = 0.16666666666666666 Fx = 5e-5

Boundary west periodic
Boundary east periodic
Boundary south wall
Boundary north wall

Refine yband { region = [0, 4, 18, 10], ratio = 2 }

Run 80 steps
Diagnostics every 20 [step, ux, uy]
